name: Crhymes - Ride Witchoo ft Krizz Kaliko (NFT Music Single)
description: This hand drawn animated illustration was created by Crhymes. It was made to go with the 1st single off the "Do You Mind? EP". The song features the legendary platinum recording artist Krizz Kaliko (Formally of Tech N9ne's Imprint Strange Music) on the chorus. The smooth instrumental was created by Wyshmaster Beats.  This piece of art come with unlockable content. With the minting of this NFT, you will receive a free download link to the lossless Wav File of the single, The original 486.6 MB .mov file of the animation and the 1400 x 1400 cover art png file. Enjoy!
